  "Regulator Statement" : "DEFAULT DECISION RENDERED OCTOBER 20, 2011 WHEREIN BROWN IS FOUND TO HAVE CAUSED AN ALTERED BANKRUPTCY DISCHARGE FORM TO BE SUBMITTED TO THE FIRM, IN VIOLATION OF NASD RULE 2110, THEREFORE HE IS BARRED FROM ASSOCIATION WITH ANY FINRA MEMBER IN ANY CAPACITY.  IF NO FURTHER ACTION IS TAKEN, DECISION IS FINAL NOVEMBER 17, 2011."
